BT 0 g /F2 20 Tf 162.0 720 Td (Chapter 7: Helping Plants Grow) Tj ET
q 0.5 G 1 w 72 710 m 540 710 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 680 Td (Underground, Droplet was pulled toward something - a tree root!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 664 Td ('The tree is drinking me up!' Droplet exclaimed as she was absorbed.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 648 Td (She traveled UP through the roots, into the trunk, and out to the leaves!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 632 Td ('I am helping this tree make food from sunlight!' Droplet said proudly.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 616 Td (When the Sun heated the leaf, Droplet evaporated back into the air again!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 600 Td ('This is called transpiration!' she shouted. 'I am going back to the sky!') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 13 Tf 72 564 Td (THE SCIENCE: TRANSPIRATION) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 544 Td (Plants absorb water from the soil through their roots.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 528 Td (Water travels up through the plant like drinking through a straw.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 512 Td (Plants use water plus sunlight plus carbon dioxide to make sugar \(food\) - photosynthesis!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 496 Td (Transpiration is when water evaporates from tiny holes in leaves \(stomata\).) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 480 Td (A large tree can release 100 gallons of water into the air per day through its leaves!) Tj ET
q 0.92 g 67 390 478 89 re f Q
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 77 449 Td (SCIENCE FACT BOX) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 82 429 Td (* A large oak tree drinks about 40,000 gallons of water from the soil each year.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 82 411 Td (* Plants release oxygen as a waste product - which is what we breathe!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 82 393 Td (* If you put a plastic bag over a leaf on a sunny day, you will see water collect inside.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 72 360 Td (TRY THIS!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 82 344 Td (Put a clear plastic bag over a leafy branch. In a few hours, see water droplets form inside!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 72 324 Td (THINK ABOUT IT:) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 10 Tf 82 308 Td (If trees release water into the air, do forests help make rain?) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
