q 0.5 G 1 w 72 710 m 540 710 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 680 Td (1. What percentage of Earth is covered by oceans?) Tj ET
BT 0.5 g /F3 9 Tf 72 662 Td (Answer: ___________________________________) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 632 Td (2. What is it called when liquid water turns into gas?) Tj ET
BT 0.5 g /F3 9 Tf 72 614 Td (Answer: ___________________________________) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 584 Td (3. What are clouds made of?) Tj ET
